\n    For i = 1 To 8\n        IsTaken(i) = 0\n    Next i\n    For k = 1 To 8\n        ChosenData = Int(Rnd() * 8 + 1)\n        Do While IsTaken(ChosenData) &lt;&gt; 0\n            ChosenData = Int(Rnd() * 8 + 1)\n        Loop\n        IsTaken(ChosenData) = 1\n        Cells(k + 1, j + 6).Value = Cells(ChosenData + 1, j).Value\n    Next k\nNext j\n\nEnd Sub\n</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"我唔識點用呢堆code<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者可唔可以你run個result 睇下有幾多個組合"},{"pid":"b346eb45b48867b95e616e0e64cec9226facfaaf","tid":1008122,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93520850e3d1f02b5a13a1d0cfff46a6d738b7e5","tid":1008122,"uid":59746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5074afa34743db8f3ffbcbd16181409e666c5401","tid":1008122,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87498b5999f7459fe9c2cc600b8dcf98d732ba09","tid":1008122,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"A1 B1 C1 D1 E1 ok<br />\nA2 B3 C4 D3 E2 ok<br />\nA3 B2 C6 D4 E5 ok<br />\nA5 B4 C4 D5 E6 唔ok?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"A1 B1 C1 D1 E1 ok<br />\nA2 B3 C4 D3 E2 ok<br />\nA3 B2 C6 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">D4 E5</span></strong> ok<br />\nA5 B4 C4 D5 E6 ok<br />\nA4 B5 C5 <span style=\"color: red;\">D4 E5</span> 就唔ok<br />\n<br />\n同上面第三組撞左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"up 咩撚野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42hTvtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42hTvtM.png&h=ffc52b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA:E 係我擁有既數據<br />\n每組(A,B,C,D,E) 各有8個數據 共5組 總數40個數據<br />\n我想係排列所有A+B+C+D+E 既組合<br />\n每次每組只能派出一個數據加入組合<br />\n而且唔可以重複曾經成為同一組合既配搭 <br />\n只有兩個成為過同組都唔得<br />\n每組都要係A+B+C+D+E 既新配搭<br />\n唔可以係之前重複成為同一組既